Redistribution (unmodified) is allowed for non-commercial purposes only, if this license file is included in full, the author's name is preserved, and no third party claims ownership.

7. No Warranty / Liability
The software is provided “as is.” No warranties, express or implied, are given. To the maximum extent allowed by law, the author excludes all liability for damages, data loss, or losses resulting from software use, non-use, or misuse.

8. License Fees
